.TH Command : BOARD
.s1
The board command enables two ships' crews to engage in hand-to-hand
combat. To board a ship type
.EX board (ship)
where (ship) is the ship number you wish to attack.
The program will ask from which ship you wish to board.
You may only board from one ship at a time...
One more problem --- you can not board a freighter while it is
in a fleet and protected by gunships...
Take note that the boarders are at a disadvantage while swinging
across to the other ship.
Weather can prevent boarding when the sea is too rough...
